    "0 (predicted noise).",
    "The noise that is added to x tÀ1 during the forward pass is predicted (approximated) by the model.As previously mentioned, several design issues are presented by the enormous class of machine learning (ML) tasks known as natural image synthesis, which has numerous applications.",
    "Image super-resolution is one instance, in which a model is trained to convert an unrefined low-resolution image into an accurate highresolution image.",
    "(e.g., RAISR).",
